Friends take a moment to decompress on the quad, sharing the positive responses they received from various companies. Meanwhile, announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair, and alumni volunteers share quick pep talks near the coffee station. Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths.
